title: House Cleaner Downtown SF
description: Armory apartments is looking for a house cleaner to clean the common areas of their apartments. This includes the kitchen, living room, and bathroom. The house cleaner will be responsible for cleaning the floors, dusting, and taking out the trash. The house cleaner will also be responsible for cleaning the windows and doing the laundry. Payment is $15 per hour, 5 hours per day maximum.

title: Golden Gate Park window cleaner wanted
description: Window cleaner needed to clean the windows of a 3 story building in Golden Gate Park. The window cleaner will be responsible for cleaning the windows, sills and screens. Payment is maximum $200 for the job.

title: Chef wanted to cook dinner for 2 adults
description: This old Victorian Home is looking for a chef to cook nightly meals for 2 adults, Mon through Thursday every week. Payment is based on 3 hours per day

title: Luxury hotel concierge needed in Financial District
description: This hotel maintains a great view of the city and we are in need of a part time concierge for 2x 5 hour shifts on the weekends.

title: Sunset District restaurant needs front of house staff
description: We are looking for 3-4 people to rotate part time shifts between waiting tables and maitre d' duties. Payment is $30 per hour plus any additional tips.
